** port number and socket
UDP socket ---------------------------
* a House: a process
* Door: socket
* Each process has 1 or n sockets
* inside side of the door:  Application Layer(Application program) where we programmer can control
* Outside side of the door: Transport Layer(when massage is pushed out of the door) 

* the destination address attached on the packet has 2 information:
1. IP addre of destination
2. the Port No. of the socket on the destination

端口号和套接字是两回事，不同的协议决定端口号不同
HTTP的端口号    80
FTP的端口号     21
Telnet的端口号  23
Mail server端口号 25


